# Heavy/derived artifacts — don't bloat the build context
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
**/*.pyc
**/*.log
**/.vite
**/coverage

# Local env files — these should be injected by Railway, not baked into images
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Git / IDE
.git
.gitignore
.github
.idea
.vscode

# Docs / specs not needed in the image
README.md
CLAUDE.md
specs/
.playwright-mcp/
